Niger’s First Oil Refinery to Be Inaugurated

-- B y   D j i b r i l   S a i d o u
-- 
2011-08-29T10:22:40Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-28/nigeria-s-first-oil-refinery-to-be-inaugurated-this-october.html
(Corrects name of country in headline and story. The story  was first published yesterday.)  Niger’s first oil refinery will
be inaugurated in October, according to broadcaster Tele
Sahel. The refinery was built by the China National
Petroleum Corporation-Niger Petroleum SA, which engages in
oil production in Niger. The company also built a pipeline
to transport crude from oil fields in Agadam to the
refinery.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Djibril Saidou via Accra at 
 Ebowers1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Antony Sguazzin at 
 asguazzin@bloomberg.net  